== 分布 ==
二水合氯化钙构成了稀有的[[蒸发岩|蒸发岩]]矿物[[水氯钙石|水氯钙石]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Sinjarite, a New Mineral from Iraq|author=Zeki A. Aljubouri and Salim M. Aldabbagh|journal=Mineralogical Magazine|year=1980|volume=43|issue=329|pages=643-646|doi=10.1180/minmag.1980.043.329.13|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=New Mineral Names|author=Michael Fleischer, Louis J. Cabri, George Y.  Cao and Adolf Pabst|url=http://www.minsocam.org/ammin/AM65/AM65_1065.pdf|journal=American  Mineralogist|volume=65|pages=1065-1070|year=1980|language=en|access-date=2012-08-25|archive-date=2011-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110905002031/http://www.minsocam.org/ammin/AM65/AM65_1065.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，蒸发岩矿物[[南极石|南极石]]则是以矿物形式存在于自然界中的六水合氯化钙<ref>{{cite journal|author=Tetsuya Torii, Joyo Ossaka|title=Antarcticite: A New Mineral, Calcium Chloride Hexahydrate, Discovered in Antarctica|journal=Science|year=1965|issue=3687|volume=149|pages=975-977|doi=10.1126/science.149.3687.975|language=en}}</ref>，其他与氯化钙有关的矿物包括同样非常稀有的[[氯钾钙石|氯钾钙石]]KCaCl<sub>3</sub><ref>Palache, C., H. Berman, and C. Frondel (1951) Dana’s system of mineralogy,(7th edition), v. II, 91–92.{{en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Chlorocalcite|url=http://www.handbookofmineralogy.org/pdfs/chlorocalcite.pdf|language=en|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2012-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120806181318/http://www.handbookofmineralogy.org/pdfs/chlorocalcite.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 应用 ==
=== 干燥剂 ===
颗粒状的无水氯化钙常作为[[干燥剂|干燥剂]]填充[[干燥管|干燥管]]<ref>{{cite journal|author=A. T. McPherson|title=Granular Calcium Chloride As A Drying Agent.|journal=J. Am. Chem. Soc.|year=1917|volume=39|issue=7|pages=1317–1319|doi=10.1021/ja02252a004|url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja02252a004|language=en|access-date=2012-08-26|archive-date=2021-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608021343/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja02252a004|dead-url=no}}</ref>，用氯化钙干燥过的[[巨藻|巨藻]]（或称海草灰）可用于[[纯碱|纯碱]]的生产。一些家用除湿器比如DampRid<ref>{{cite web|title=Moisture Absorbing Products - How DampRid Works|url=http://www.damprid.com/moisture-prevention/how-damprid-works|accessdate=2012-09-22|language=en|archive-date=2012-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017043400/http://www.damprid.com/moisture-prevention/how-damprid-works|dead-url=no}}</ref>会使用氯化钙吸收空气中的水分。氯化钙还可作为气体和有机液体的干燥剂或脱水剂。由于氯化钙是中性的，因此它可以干燥酸性或碱性的气体和有机液体，可也在实验室制取少量气体如[[氮|氮]]气、[[氧气|氧气]]、[[氢气|氢气]]、[[氯化氢|氯化氢]]、[[二氧化硫|二氧化硫]]、[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]、[[二氧化氮|二氧化氮]]等时干燥这些制出的气体。但不能用来干燥[[乙醇|乙醇]]和[[氨|氨]]，因为乙醇和氨气分别会与氯化钙反应生成醇合物CaCl<sub>2</sub>·4C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>5</sub>OH和氨合物CaCl<sub>2</sub>·8NH<sub>3</sub><ref>{{cite book|title=I.I.T. Chemistry|author=Dr. P. B. Saxena|publisher =Publisher Krishna Prakashan Media|pages=283|language=en}}</ref><ref name=wjhx_p34 />。无水氯化钙还可被制成家用产品用作空气吸湿剂，无水氯化钙作为吸水剂已被[[美国食品药品监督管理局|FDA]]批准用于包扎急救，它的作用是确保创口处的干燥<ref>{{cite web
